@page "/"

<PageTitle>StockSight</PageTitle>

<section class="dashboard-hero fade-in">
    <div class="hero-copy">
        <span class="eyebrow">Realtime market workspace</span>
        <h1 class="hero-title">Read price action, signals, and portfolio risk in one dark console.</h1>
        <p class="lead">
            StockSight brings live quotes, technical overlays, backtests, portfolio P&amp;L, and alert workflows into a compact Blazor dashboard built for repeated market checks.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
            <NavLink class="primary-button" href="watchlist">Open watchlist</NavLink>
            <NavLink class="secondary-button" href="stock/AAPL">View AAPL chart</NavLink>
        </div>
    </div>

    <aside class="hero-market-strip" aria-label="StockSight capabilities">
        <article class="market-tile">
            <span class="status-pill live">Live SignalR quotes</span>
            <strong class="num">AAPL 250.33</strong>
            <span class="up">▲ Streaming tick updates</span>
        </article>
        <article class="market-tile">
            <span class="status-pill">Technical stack</span>
            <strong>RSI, MACD, SMA, EMA</strong>
            <span class="status">Candles stay front and center.</span>
        </article>
        <article class="market-tile">
            <span class="status-pill warn">Risk loop</span>
            <strong>Backtest to portfolio</strong>
            <span class="status">Run a strategy, then track P&amp;L and alerts.</span>
        </article>
    </aside>
</section>

<section class="dashboard-grid">
    <article class="surface">
        <div class="surface-header">
            <h2>Market scan</h2>
            <span class="status-pill live">Realtime</span>
        </div>
        <p class="page-lead">Watch default symbols, add your own tickers, and jump directly into a detail chart when price moves.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="surface">
        <div class="surface-header">
            <h2>Signal context</h2>
            <span class="status-pill">Indicators</span>
        </div>
        <p class="page-lead">Candles, overlays, RSI, MACD, and news sentiment share one view so signals have context instead of noise.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="surface">
        <div class="surface-header">
            <h2>Execution loop</h2>
            <span class="status-pill">Portfolio</span>
        </div>
        <p class="page-lead">Use backtests, paper trades, position allocation, and alerts to keep decisions connected.</p>
    </article>
</section>
